text:
On the 15th March, Amazon Linux 2023 made its debut. This latest version comes with three significant features:

To learn more about IMDS, check out my blog: https://lnkd.in/gnTA_brw ‚Ä¢ AL2023 utilizes gp3 volumes by default, reducing costs with improved performance. ‚Ä¢ Versioned repositories offer more control over packages, allowing for better standardization of workloads.
